name: Watcher
description:
I felt a strong urge to paint something more contrasting and dynamic, and I guess it reflects a
bit of how life has been recently. I’m either feeling energized, upbeat and in control, or utterly
tired and over it. But things have still been coming together and a year’s worth of hard work
and conflict has been calming down and producing some very good results.
{6364x9000}
